Description:

The ftpd tool allows the user to create an ftp daemon that listens on a specified port on the client. It can be used to access the Grid namespace and resources via the FTP protocol.

The following options are available:

--idle-timeout=<secs>

--data-connection-timeout=<secs>

--max-auth-attempts=<number>

--sandbox=<path>

stop

Stops the ftp daemon on the client.

